==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[sulfur]] [[dioxide]]'''
#{{chemistry}} a [[toxic]] [[gas]], of [[molecular formula]] SO<sub>2</sub> that is found in the [[emission]]s of [[volcano]]s and those of burning [[coal]] or [[petroleum]]; dissolves in water to form [[sulfurous acid]] and, in the presence of [[oxygen]], [[sulfuric acid]], and is thus responsible for [[acid rain]]
